{"tid":2429951,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方國安處拘捕壹傳媒前執行董事丁家裕 涉違串謀欺詐案　","createTime":"2021-03-02T15:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T00:08:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"ff986dd36fbb250eedd28619b8c1ba049ce778bc","tid":2429951,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"警方國家安全處人員於去年8月10日持法庭手令，大舉搜查《蘋果日報》位於將軍澳的廠房，並在全港多區10人，包括壹傳媒黎智英、其兩名兒子黎見恩及黎耀恩。據了解，國安處經進一步調查後，今日（2日）在中區拘捕一名61歲姓丁的男子涉嫌「欺詐」，他現正被扣留調查，令案件被捕人數增至11人。   <br />\n<br />\n消息指，被捕男子為丁家裕，為壹傳媒前執行董事，在壹傳媒任職長達18年，是集團老臣子，丁於2015年9月突然請辭，同時辭去集團營運總裁、財務總裁與薪酬委員會成員的職務。當時有證券分析員表示，事件耐人尋味，而高層「跳船」難免令投資者憂慮公司前景。"},{"pid":"44ed2bcb3148b11864e8b5da186441b1b69a72a0","tid":2429951,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1deac6410a489da3f89432099e2053cae2c7b5","tid":2429951,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353e3a9c63b23eac949175a73deb5f9ec70fa791","tid":2429951,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f93f335622f98460d1f34f5124cd567fa570368","tid":2429951,"uid":205967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim